{"tid":1470781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不需擔心風向問題、冷處理、聚焦818","createTime":"2019-08-14T06:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T11:49:11.000Z","uid":85924,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1691899c66367d86decc7ec1b6e00eced8d4889b","tid":1470781,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:38:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不需擔心風向問題</span></span><br />\n去到而家，一單咁所謂打記單事件對成個風向影響根本微不足道，要撐一早撐左，要屌亦一早屌左。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冷處理</span></span><br />\n政府平處理問題會點？冷處理。佢地會慢慢耍太極，顧左右而言他，耍多兩耍就冇人記得，我地都要做一樣既野。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聚焦818<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n距離818仲有幾日，你地想全個連登都係互屌post定818 post? 政府唔怕你互屌，唔怕你咩機場道歉，只怕你818多人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全連登聚焦818</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209b0d2e36a33f55a74d31e47d055b9ad80c71da","tid":1470781,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:38:44.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"ffca2232ad57e2891dfbc2d0d5ff230878734480","tid":1470781,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:38:55.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"c40ed13c6fe4e9dfa4f60798e27d08b3ca2031ce","tid":1470781,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:39:57.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"1556549dfbd313f8ff2faf6764caf517130c5532","tid":1470781,"uid":230911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:40:04.000Z","msg":"一個818 post 都推唔到上黎丫"},{"pid":"a6e9b190556105b31f5e01bbbca9a27da893b8e1","tid":1470781,"uid":245371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:40:17.000Z","msg":"[思想改革] 抗爭